2026-03-29T16:02:05.8781228Z               "id": "bc3ce545909602700b160eb68259ed55480e1c1e",
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8783912Z               "message": "Refactor build logs from per-build branches to single orphan branch\n\nStore all build logs as folders on a single `build-logs` orphan branch\ninstead of creating a separate orphan branch per build. Each build becomes\na folder named `<run>-<id>-<timestamp>-<status>`. Old folders are pruned\nto keep only the 10 most recent.\n\nThe GitHub Action uses `--filter=blob:none` to avoid downloading existing\nlog content when adding new builds. The skill uses blobless fetches with\n`-c` config overrides to read only the specific files needed without\npolluting the user's repo config.\n\nConcurrent build races are handled by a retry loop (up to 3 attempts\nwith backoff) that re-fetches and re-applies on push failure.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01YcBBPy1V3viff4r3qBtUgA",
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8786706Z               "timestamp": "2026-03-29T15:25:15Z",
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8787005Z               "tree_id": "3431e705ee22168e469c5c0cc39877a45fb25559",
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8787500Z               "url": "https://github.com/***/hpoll/commit/bc3ce545909602700b160eb68259ed55480e1c1e"
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8788011Z             },
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8788307Z             {
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8788583Z               "author": {
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8789011Z                 "email": "noreply@anthropic.com",
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8789560Z                 "name": "Claude",
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8789920Z                 "username": "claude"
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8790241Z               },
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8790420Z               "committer": {
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8790639Z                 "email": "noreply@anthropic.com",
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8790890Z                 "name": "Claude",
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8791104Z                 "username": "claude"
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8791305Z               },
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8791487Z               "distinct": false,
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8791747Z               "id": "e42b375f4b2b8e330e76ce7fe6afb6249937597d",
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8793969Z               "message": "Fix build-logs push: delete old-format branches and fix retry logic\n\nTwo issues caused the push-build-logs step to fail:\n\n1. Namespace conflict: Git refs can't be both a leaf and a directory,\n   so refs/heads/build-logs can't coexist with refs/heads/build-logs/296-*.\n   Fix: delete all old-format build-logs/* branches via GitHub API before\n   attempting to push.\n\n2. Retry bug: after a failed push, git rm --cached cleared the index but\n   HEAD still pointed to the committed tree, so re-adding the folder made\n   the index match HEAD again (\"nothing to commit\"). Fix: reset to orphan\n   state at the start of each retry attempt.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01YcBBPy1V3viff4r3qBtUgA",
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8796280Z               "timestamp": "2026-03-29T15:33:30Z",
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8796584Z               "tree_id": "3956bfae4128f799401924c6809c15405a8168d8",
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8797058Z               "url": "https://github.com/***/hpoll/commit/e42b375f4b2b8e330e76ce7fe6afb6249937597d"
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8797432Z             },
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8797591Z             {
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8797757Z               "author": {
