2026-03-29T16:02:05.8800116Z               "id": "bf901b4f2c119a8b5e2dbcea3cba223e9d5dcb54",
2026-03-29T16:02:05.8801385Z               "message": "Strengthen polling instructions to prevent async fire-and-forget loop\n\nAdd explicit warnings that polling is synchronous (blocking wait for\ntask-notification), not asynchronous. Call out the specific mistake of\nreading the output file immediately after launching the background task.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01YcBBPy1V3viff4r3qBtUgA",
